[1:2] All joy count `it&rsquo;, my brethren, when ye may fall into temptations manifold;
[1:3] knowing that the proof of your faith doth work endurance,
[1:4] and let the endurance have a perfect work, that ye may be perfect and entire &ndash; in nothing lacking;
